                     <interp inst="t18310630-55-person504" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have the handkerchief, pawned by the witness at our shop, for 2s. 6d., in the name of 
               <persName id="t18310630-55-person505">
                  John 
                  Chandler
